Private Sub AbaAlmHistorico_Click()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim TAG_INSTRUMENTO As String
TAG_INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_")
' AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "'" FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim TAG_INSTRUMENTO As String
TAG_INSTRUMENTO = Replace(Text1.Caption, "-", "_")
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "'" ' FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & TAG_INSTRUMENTO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
Private Sub NumericInput_SP_KeyDown(ByVal KeyCode As Integer, ByVal Shift As Integer)
If KeyCode = vbKeyReturn Then SendKeys "{F1}" End If
End Sub
